  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study was to assess the incidence of side effects after direct-acting
      antiviral therapy in patients with chronic hepatitis C virus infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Direct-acting antiviral (DAA)-based treatments are today very effective The objective of this
      study was to assess the incidence of side effects after DAA therapy in patients with chronic
      hepatitis C virus infection.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
